{"title":"gitbook使用","date":"2023-06-15T16:36:28.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 16, 2023","L":"06/16/2023","MM-DD":"06-16"},"link":"2023/06/16/gitbook使用","updated":"2023-06-15T17:19:14.093Z","content":"<h3 id=\"gitbook使用\">Gitbook使用<a title=\"#gitbook使用\" href=\"#gitbook使用\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"创建简单的gitbook\">创建简单的gitbook<a title=\"#创建简单的gitbook\" href=\"#创建简单的gitbook\"></a></h4>\n<p>为电子书创建目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> my-gitbook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>执行<code>gitbook init</code>命令，初始化电子书目录，执行结束后会出现<code>SUMMARY.md</code>和<code>README.md</code>文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gitbook init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>生成动态网页，执行<code>gitbook server</code>启动web服务，默认端口4000</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gitbook server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>浏览器输入<code>http://localhost:4000</code>，访问该电子书</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>其他详细配置链接：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41809023/article/details/127514108\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41809023/article/details/127514108</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>生成静态网页，静态HTML会输出到<code>_book</code>目录中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gitbook build</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"解决gitbook-build静态网页无法跳转问题\">解决gitbook build静态网页无法跳转问题<a title=\"#解决gitbook-build静态网页无法跳转问题\" href=\"#解决gitbook-build静态网页无法跳转问题\"></a></h4>\n<p>在_book文件夹内，找到gitbook文件夹，在里面找到theme.js</p>\n<p>用文本搜索工具查找</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(m)<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(n.<span class=\"property\">handler</span>&amp;&amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将<code>if(m)</code>改成<code>if(false)</code></p>\n<p>再次打开_book下的网页，就可以正常跳转了</p>\n","prev":{"title":"考研英语复习","link":"2023/08/26/考研英语复习"},"next":{"title":"leetcode","link":"2023/05/12/leetcode"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/06/16/gitbook使用/","toc":[{"id":"gitbook使用","title":"Gitbook使用","index":"1"}],"copyright":{"custom":"my copyright"},"reading_time":"198 words in 1 min"}